Theorem. (SNoS_ordsucc_omega_bdd_eps_pos)

Theorem. (real_complete1)
∀a b ∈ realω, (∀n ∈ ω, a n ≤ b n ∧ a n ≤ a (ordsucc n) ∧ b (ordsucc n) ≤ b n) → ∃x ∈ real, ∀n ∈ ω, a n ≤ x ∧ x ≤ b n
